<bibRefCitation author="World Spider Catalog" box="[1052,1378,383,408]" pageId="9" pageNumber="46" refId="ref5909" refString="World Spider Catalog (2018) World Spider Catalog. Version 19.0. Natural History Museum Bern. Available from: http: // wsc. nmbe. ch (accessed 30 July 2018)" type="url" year="2018">World Spider Catalog, 2018</bibRefCitation>
